What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Precision Viticulture Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Global Precision Viticulture Market

Precision viticulture market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2022-2029. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to account to grow at a CAGR of 8.60% and is likely to reach USD 2.73 billion in 2029.

Precision viticulture identifies & maintains variability at intervals vineyards, preciseness viticulture is a scientific technique widely used by massive wineries to manage the big variety of farm areas. Farm helps in increasing grape yield and quality safeguarding it from environmental risk.

Big support provided by government regarding viticulture techniques is the major factor accelerating the growth of the market. Furthermore, rising demand for high quality grapes, advancements in new techniques to maximize the profits are also expected to drive the growth of the precision viticulture market. However, lack of technical awareness & high capital investment restrains the precision viticulture market, whereas, lack of skilled workers to perform viticulture techniques will challenge market growth.

In addition, modernization in techniques and increased productivity will create ample opportunities for the precision viticulture market.

